   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BITS ETC --We are still here!</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">From clients with autism, to volunteers who struggle with ADHD, and board members who are themselves physically disabled, we &quot;walk the walk&quot; at BITS ETC, encouraging those who come here with what is called a disability, to pursue a quality of life that we all deserve.    The pursuit of happiness for many, starts on the back of a horse.  BITS ETC provides the well trained equine partners in the process.  Your donation will support the care of our horses and the programs that serve our clients.</narrative>
  </description>
